channel.title: Having problems with getting my server online
channel.description:
I've done everything, portfoward, no-ip and no-ip DUC, i have JDK 6u3 and it works proper
Portfoward
[IMG]http://i272.photobucket.com/albums/jj168/Camoboii/Portfoward-1.jpg[/img]
No-ip DUC
[IMG]http://i272.photobucket.com/albums/jj168/Camoboii/No-ipDUC.jpg[/img]
It lets people [b] under my internet connection get on using my Computers IP [/b] (the ip that i opened ports for) But it seems that my no-ip is useless and has no effect, how do i make my no-ip work so anyone could connect using my no-ip?
EDIT: I'm getting off 2 go to bed so tomorrow i will check this out, also, before you post please take time 2 [b] read the whole thing [/b] and please no [b] spam [/b]
